name: Overworld
resume:
Venture into the vast and blocky Overworld, a land of forests, mountains, oceans, and mysteries.
   Survive, build, and explore a terrain shaped by nature and creativity.
presentation:
Step into the endlessly generating world of the Overworld, where survival meets creativity.
From lush forests to deep ravines, village trading to dungeon crawling, this world offers limitless adventure.

Discover hidden strongholds, master the art of crafting and redstone, and encounter friendly villagers and hostile mobs.

Whether you're a builder, an explorer, or a fighter, the Overworld is your gateway to an unforgettable journey.

schedule.description1:
Traverse through plains, deserts, jungles, and snowy peaks.
   Each biome holds unique resources and secrets to discover.
schedule.description2:
Visit peaceful villages and interact with local villagers.
   Trade goods, protect the town, and learn the lore of the land.

schedule.description1:
Descend into massive cave systems to gather rare ores.
   Beware of creepers and hidden dangers in the dark.
schedule.description2:
Explore ancient jungle and desert temples.
   Solve puzzles and disarm traps to claim hidden treasures.

schedule.description1:
Build your own portal to unlock interdimensional travel.
   Learn about obsidian, flint & steel, and travel logistics.

Join a party to locate a hidden stronghold.
   Discover the End Portal and prepare for a future journey beyond the Overworld.
schedule.description2:
Put your skills to the test in a final creative challenge.
   Construct a base, tower, or redstone machine with the resources gathered.
